parameters: This should be the deepest part...
Yeah, it should be around here...
Is this monster definitely our hunting target?
Captain, I'm counting on you! Please take it down quickly!
Relying on others from the start, I see.

Well, it's fine. A monster of this level won't give me any
trouble.
Oh! You cornered it in no time.
Of course. Didn't I say it wouldn't be a problem?

If we don't need to capture it alive, may I finish it off
now?
What are you doing!? You're in the way!
I was going to finish off a dying monster like that!
Ahhh~ It hurts~ It really hurts~
Because you screwed up, Captain, I got injured...
What are you saying...!? Are you blaming me...!?

You're the one who bumped into me! If you hadn't interfered,
I would have definitely killed it!
Huh? Making excuses after injuring me?

Ahh~ It really hurts~ First things first, we should treat
it, right?

There are no major external injuries; I can't tell about
internal ones though...

But why are you talking like it's someone else's problem
after injuring me?
You don't think this kind of treatment is enough, do you?
Tch... Are you saying it's my fault after all...

I'm not saying I'm completely blameless... but what are you
getting at...?
Well, if you feel bad about it, you should apologize, right?

It's kind of weird to do this here, but could you listen to
one request of mine?\I[12]

I feel good after getting off, so maybe I'll let it end here
for now\I[12]
What do you mean...? It should be over already...
Hey hey, you don't think it ends with just this, do you?

I'm injured here, so you're going to help with the hunt and
take care of my cock too\I[12]
Wha...!? Why should I have to do all that...!?

Can't be helped, right? What if forcing it makes the injury
worse?

It's only until the injury heals, so you're not going to say
you'll shirk your responsibility, right?

Understood... I'll take care of you if that's what you
want...

But only until your injury heals! I absolutely refuse to do
anything beyond that!
I get it, I get it. So we have a deal then\I[12]
